        <briefdescription>
<para>Close the session and release any resources. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This method is called when the session is no longer needed. For stateful sessions (e.g., OAuth2 with token refresh), this should stop any background threads and release resources.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Status indicating success or failure of closing the session. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
