        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This factory method creates a session that adds a fixed set of headers to each request. It is suitable for authentication methods that use static credentials, such as Basic auth or static bearer tokens.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>headers</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The headers to add to each request for authentication. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>A new session that adds the given headers to requests. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
